@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Rule";
    Layout = null;
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>游戏规则</title>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no,minimal-ui" name="viewport">
        <meta content="yes" name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable">
        <meta content="black" name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style">
        <meta content="telephone=no" name="format-detection">
        <meta content="email=no" name="format-detection">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/reset.css" />
        <link href="~/css/MoreMemberMobile.css" rel="stylesheet" />
        <link href="~/css/MoreMember.css" rel="stylesheet" />
        <link href="~/css/MoreMemberMobile.css" rel="stylesheet" />
        <style type="text/css">
            .choose_btn {
                width: 70%;
                background: url('/Img/MoreMember/green.png') repeat-x;
                color: #ffffff;
                border: 0px;
                height: 30px;
            }

            .choose {
                position: fixed;
                top: 40%;
                text-align: center;
                width: 300px;
                height: 220px;
                background: url('/Img/MoreMember/alertbg.png') no-repeat;
            }
        </style>
        <script src="~/Scripts/jquery-1.10.2.min.js"></script>
        <script src="~/Content/layer/layer.min.js"></script>
        <script>
            $(function () {
                var objlyear = null;
                //判断是否登录
                $("#startGame").click(function () {
                    $.ajax({
                        url: "/MoreMemberMobile/GetLogin",
                        type: "get",
                        success: function (result) {
                            if (result.msg == "true") { //已登录
                                location.href = "/MoreMemberMobile/Game";
                            }
                            else {  //未登录
                                objlyear = $.layer({
                                    type: 1,   //0-4的选择,
                                    title: false,
                                    border: [0],
                                    closeBtn: [0],
                                    shadeClose: false,
                                    area: ['92%', ''],
                                    page: { dom: '.choose' }
                                });
                            }
                            $(".xubox_shade").click(function () {
                                layer.close(objlyear);
                            })
                        },
                        error: function () {

                        }

                    })


                });
                $(".wati").click(function () {
                    layer.close(objlyear);
                })
                //登录注册跳转
                $("#register").click(function () {
                    layer.close(objlyear);
                    var returnUrl = "/MoreMemberMobile/Game";
                    location.href = "/WapQuestionnaire/WapRegister?returnUrl=" + encodeURIComponent(returnUrl);
                })
                $("#login").click(function () {
                    layer.close(objlyear);
                    var returnUrl = "/MoreMemberMobile/Game";
                    location.href = "/WapQuestionnaire/WapLogin?returnUrl=" + encodeURIComponent(returnUrl);
                })
            })
        </script>
    </head>
    <body class="ruleBody">
        <div id="wrap">
            <div class="title" style="height:18px; width:100%;">
            </div>
            <div id="ruleTit" class="ruleTit">
                <span>游戏规则</span>
            </div>
            <div id="content">
                <p>在闽南地区4是福气如意的意思，所以以骰子中4点为标准评判获奖等级；具体规则如下：</p>
                <p>1、两枚骰子点数相同且均为4点为状元，对应礼品为三星Gear 2 Neo智能手表</p>
                <p>2、两枚骰子点数相同但不是4点为榜眼，对应礼品为卓棒Jawbone UP24智能手环</p>
                <p>3、两枚骰子中有一枚为4点另一枚点数大于4为探花，对应礼品为旅行收纳四件套</p>
                <p>4、两枚骰子中有一枚为4点另一枚点数小于4为进士，对应礼品为卡片式移动电源</p>
                <p>5、两枚骰子点数均大于4点为举人，对应礼品为车载usb充电器</p>
            </div>
            <div id="footer">
                <a href="/MoreMemberMobile/introduction" id="introduction">
                    活动介绍
                </a>
                <a href="#" id="startGame">开始游戏</a>
            </div>
            <div class="choose" style="display:none">
                <span>
                    <a href="#" id="login"><input type="button" style="  margin-top: 80px;" class="choose_btn" value="登录" /></a>
                    <a href="#" id="register"><input type="button" style="margin-top:15px;" class="choose_btn" value="注册" /></a>

                </span>
                <div style="margin-top:20px;">
                    <a href="" class="wati">稍后再说</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>


